{"data":[{"id":560978794,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8c0b619de43f1583004c834d154cce33","url_token":"qian-feng-81-27","name":"深海逐豚","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5c2e7ca7afa7f98e4a848ec72964c5a0_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5c2e7ca7afa7f98e4a848ec72964c5a0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8c0b619de43f1583004c834d154cce33","user_type":"people","headline":"理想主义中的悲观生活者。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":8,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560978794","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545903980,"updated_time":1545973098,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果是我，看到题目，我会答题：略。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得题主的问题应该表达错了，或者表达不清楚。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e应该是，一个高中生喜欢钻研数学问题，平时也很喜欢看其他大佬解题的思路，包括其他人证明猜想但不准确的过程，但其实自己是做不出来的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e突然有一天，碰巧证明了哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而让这位高中生完全重新做一次，他做不出来，他甚至无法完全回答提问者的问题，但他能拿出一个完全正确的解题方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就像玄幻小说《大主宰》里，主角参加大千盟组织的大千会，在小世界里争夺功法和宝物，小世界里有邪魔，邪魔分为魔王，魔帝，天魔帝等。大千盟有一个规定，只要大千世界的人杀一个邪魔，就能给自己的身份牌加积分，而杀了天魔帝的人，就可以直接成为诛魔王。主角功力还不够，在最后时刻，让自己已经死去但镇压着天魔帝的祖先附体，最后终于打败了天魔帝，而主角想起大千会那个规定，跟祖先说，让自己用令牌收一丝天魔帝的魂试一下能不能成功，然后直接成为第二位诛魔王。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第一位诛魔王是一个一个打上去的，段位为大千世界最高几人之一。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后的结果是，大千会承认了主角诛魔王的身份，但因为其本身能力的不足，大千盟无法为其提供其他实质性帮助，不会给主角提供药材，功法，仆人等等，只给了一个让别人不好明面动主角的名号。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，你觉得呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好吧，我只是不相信题主能证明而已。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而如果你真的证明出哥猜，北大清华不是保送，而是特邀。国外top大学也会争夺，因为你是数学界一颗闪闪发亮的新星。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大佬，我等你论证过程。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"谢邀。如果是我，看到题目，我会答题：略。我觉得题主的问题应该表达错了，或者表达不清楚。应该是，一个高中生喜欢钻研数学问题，平时也很喜欢看其他大佬解题的思路，包括其他人证明猜想但不准确的过程，但其实自己是做不出来的。突然有一天，碰巧证明了哥…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=752\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Cresh